<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3967346>
    dc:description "Figs. 1-7. Seasonal abundance of nymphs and adults of the most common pentatomids found on privet Ligustrum lucidum during a one-year period in northern Paraná state, Brazil." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3967346/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3967352>
    dc:description "Figs. 13-16. 13, Adult of Pallantia macunaima on a privet leaf. 14-16, Pellaea stictica: 14, adult on mature on privet leaf; 15, fifth instar on mature fruits of privet; 16, egg mass on a privet leaf.(Scales: 4mm, fig. 13; 5mm, fig. 14; 1mm, figs. 15-16)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3967352/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

